        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl max-w-[30ch]">
          Front end developer, studying to become full stack.
        </p>
        <button class="w-fit h-fit hover:-translate-y-[10px] transition-all"
          ><a
            href="#footer"
            class="border border-text bg-bg px-4 py-2 text-3xl max-md:text-2xl rounded transition-all hover:drop-shadow-accentSh hover:border-accent"
            >Contact</a
          ></button
